taxpayers' investment in their training."By reducing the number of training places for adult nurses next year, we can invest in training more nurses where London really needs them - like increasing the number of health visitors and children's nurses working in the capital."More on This StoryRelated StoriesYour view: Patient care plans06 JANUARY 2012,
